msgid "Logging"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../src/guide/platform_nixos/logging.md:10
msgid ""
"Creating, storing, and analysing logs from components and your "
"application is an important part of keeping your service healthy and "
"developing it further."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../src/guide/platform_nixos/logging.md:13
msgid ""
"On the most basic level, our {ref}`managed components <nixos-components>`"
" log to the systemd journal or provide regular log files. Log files are "
"rotated by {ref}`nixos-logrotate` which can also be configured for custom"
" log files."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../src/guide/platform_nixos/logging.md:18
msgid ""
"For more advanced use cases, you can choose to use the managed "
"{ref}`loghost <nixos-loghost>` component which uses "
"[Graylog](http://www.graylog.org) for centralized log collection."
msgstr ""

